Similar comparison as presented in Fig. 3a has been repeated for d = 1.5 nm to 196 nm and the results are discussed in terms of an emission enhancement factor (EF) as follows. The EF for the samples with different GaAs thicknesses is evaluated independently by calculating the integrated PL intensity ratio as follows.1EF=IInAs/AuNRIInAs\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
